  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      341.18,
      526.2,
      356.99
    ],
    "text": "This Court, having carefully considered the above definition, is of the view that the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      361.1,
      526.24,
      376.91
    ],
    "text": "following requirements must be satisfied by the Petitioner if it is to be excluded from",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      380.9,
      526.27,
      396.71
    ],
    "text": "the definition of industry or service, and thereby not be liable for the payment of",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      400.7,
      179.25,
      416.51
    ],
    "text": "the said allowance:",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      420.62,
      526.2,
      452.27
    ],
    "text": "a) The industry, business or undertaking must be carried out by any corporation,",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1",
      "CIDFont+F3"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      100.32,
      456.26,
      509.5,
      472.07
    ],
    "text": "board or other body which was or is established by or under any written law;",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      476.06,
      526.23,
      507.83
    ],
    "text": "b) The Government must hold a majority of the share capital in the said industry,",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1",
      "CIDFont+F3"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      100.32,
      511.82,
      526.2,
      527.63
    ],
    "text": "business or undertaking with funds or capital wholly or partly provided by the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      100.32,
      531.62,
      354.09,
      547.43
    ],
    "text": "Government by way of grant, loan or otherwise",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      571.34,
      526.26,
      587.15
    ],
    "text": "As noted at the outset, the Petitioner has admitted that the Petitioner is carrying out",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1",
      "CIDFont+F2"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      591.14,
      526.21,
      606.95
    ],
    "text": "its business in the name of Grand Oriental Hotel. Thus, on its own admission, the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1",
      "CIDFont+F2",
      "CIDFont+F4"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      610.94,
      526.31,
      626.75
    ],
    "text": "business to which the Act has been applied, and to which P2 and P4 relates to, is",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1",
      "CIDFont+F2"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      630.86,
      526.2,
      646.67
    ],
    "text": "being carried out by the Petitioner, and not by the Bank of Ceylon. For the exclusion",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      650.66,
      526.19,
      666.47
    ],
    "text": "to apply, the requirement of the Act is that the business must be carried out by the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      670.46,
      526.17,
      686.27
    ],
    "text": "entity in which the Government holds the majority of the shares. This Court is of the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      690.38,
      526.23,
      706.19
    ],
    "text": "view that the exclusion cannot be extended to entities where shares are not held by",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      710.18,
      526.22,
      725.99
    ],
    "text": "the Government, but by entities in which the Government holds the majority of the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      729.98,
      526.24,
      745.79
    ],
    "text": "shares. Thus, this Court is of the view that the above exclusion does not apply to the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      749.9,
      436.65,
      765.71
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner, as the Petitioner has failed to meet the first requirement.",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      776.62,
      525.99,
      805.9
    ],
    "text": "5",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.000450134277344
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      91.82,
      526.23,
      107.63
    ],
    "text": "Furthermore, the requirement is that the majority of the shares must be held by the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      111.74,
      526.24,
      127.55
    ],
    "text": "Government in the entity that is engaged in the industry, business or undertaking.",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      131.54,
      526.24,
      147.35
    ],
    "text": "While the Government holds the majority shares in the Bank of Ceylon, it is admitted",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      151.34,
      526.27,
      167.15
    ],
    "text": "that it is not the Government, but the Bank of Ceylon that holds the majority shares",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      171.26,
      526.34,
      187.07
    ],
    "text": "in the Petitioner. In the light of the above conclusion of this Court that the business",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      191.06,
      526.23,
      206.87
    ],
    "text": "of the Grand Oriental Hotel is being carried out by the Petitioner, and not by the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      210.86,
      526.21,
      226.67
    ],
    "text": "Bank of Ceylon, it is the view of this Court that the Petitioner has failed to meet the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      230.66,
      494.5,
      246.47
    ],
    "text": "second requirement that must be satisfied in order to qualify for the exclusion.",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      270.38,
      526.31,
      286.19
    ],
    "text": "This Court must also note that P2 and P4 refer to the Petitioner, and not the Bank",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1",
      "CIDFont+F2"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      290.18,
      526.29,
      305.99
    ],
    "text": "of Ceylon, as the employer. Furthermore, representations in P3 were made on",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1",
      "CIDFont+F2"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      310.1,
      526.21,
      325.91
    ],
    "text": "behalf of the Petitioner, and not the Bank of Ceylon, which confirms that it is the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      329.9,
      526.28,
      345.71
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner who is the employer. This too demonstrates that the provisions of the Act",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      349.7,
      526.26,
      365.51
    ],
    "text": "have been made applicable to employees of the Petitioner, and not the Bank of",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      369.62,
      114.23,
      385.43
    ],
    "text": "Ceylon.",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      409.22,
      526.24,
      425.03
    ],
    "text": "The learned Senior Deputy Solicitor General submitted that an employer can claim",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      429.02,
      526.23,
      444.83
    ],
    "text": "the benefit of the above exclusion only if it is a corporation, board or body which is",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      448.94,
      526.15,
      464.75
    ],
    "text": "established by or under any written law. He submitted that the Petitioner has been",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      468.74,
      526.21,
      484.55
    ],
    "text": "incorporated in terms of the Companies Act and therefore does not satisfy the",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      488.54,
      526.32,
      504.35
    ],
    "text": "requirement that it must be a body which is established by or under any written law.",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      508.46,
      526.19,
      524.27
    ],
    "text": "However, the necessity for this Court to consider the said submission does not arise",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      528.26,
      312.64,
      544.07
    ],
    "text": "in view of the above conclusion of this Court.",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      567.98,
      526.27,
      583.79
    ],
    "text": "In the above circumstances, this Court does not see any legal basis to issue notice of",
    "fonts": [
      "CIDFont+F1"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960525512695312
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      587.78,
      526.22,
      603.59
